text: Kairi Himanen (born 11 November 1992) is an Estonian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Naiste Meistriliiga club Pärnu. She has represented the Estonia women's national football team at youth and senior level. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Estonian women's footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Estonia women's international footballers
